videos.description: UCF get the ball to Taco Fall inside and he is denied twice, by Ben Emelogu II  and Ben Moore.
videos.headline: Taco Fall  denied twice at the rim

videos.description: B.J. Taylor goes up and under for the finish at the rim as he is fouled.

videos.description: B.J. Taylor has another nice finish at the rim with a layup off the glass as he is fouled.
